==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Palatial
<hw>Pa*la"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>palatium</ets> palace. See <er>Palace</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to a palace; suitable for a palace; resembling a palace;
royal; magnificent; <as>as, <ex>palatial</ex> structures</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Palatial</xex> style.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>A.
Drummond.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

